item.title: Vince Guaraldi Trio - Christmas Time Is Here - Key of F - ukeplayalongs
item.description: Play along video for the song Christmas Time Is Here by Vince Guaraldi Trio from the channel ukeplayalongs. Chords used in the song: A7♯5, Am7, A♭m7, Bm7♭5, C6, C7♯5, Cmaj7, D7, Fmaj7, Gm, Gm7, Gm7♭5.

item.title: Instrumental - One Note Samba - Key of C - Ukulele Underground
